* {{ill|1859|ja|1859th year|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1859|qq=}} ({{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ansei|qq=}} 6), established.
